The slowing rate of the Russian economy’s decline over the past five quarters indicates that “one has passed”.
Among other markers indicating the signs of revitalization of the national economy, Bloomberg calls the increase in demand for electricity and rail transport, the revitalization of business.
If you make an amendment to the fact that the year is high, it is clear that the dynamics in plus 1% of electricity consumption can be half due to an additional working day.
