The payment of insurance compensation to depositary of the bank, including individual entrepreneurs, in accordance with the Federal Law No. 177-FZ "On insurance of deposits of individuals in banks of the Russian Federation" is provided in the amount of 100% of the remainder of funds, but not more than 1.4 million rubles.
